Description: guided health breaks, training and local screen-time analytics
 Zdorovo schedules configurable eye, movement and posture breaks during active
 computer work. It also provides progressive training courses, breathing
 sessions, habit reminders, local per-application screen-time analytics and
 wellbeing history.
 .
 All usage data stays in the user's home directory.
